SIO output buffer mode
GPIO (General Purpose Input Output) » Macros

General Description

Constants to be used for setting the SIO output buffer mode on the pin.

Macros

#define CY_SIO_VREG_UNREGULATED   (0x00UL)
 Unregulated output buffer.
 
#define CY_SIO_VREG_REGULATED   (0x01UL)
 Regulated output buffer.
